<br>
The problem with FFA is that more then likely when you go up there won't be mobs up, or if there are mobs up there will be fair and they will be random.  People seem to have it in their minds that if we go FFA more mobs will be up when they port up more often.  When in reality, it will be just the opposite.  Instead of non stop pulls of static spawns, you'll have non stop roamers and few static spawns(with armor or epic pieces) to kill.  FFA also means that any person can go in and solo if they want to and claim loots.  If they want to solo next to your group, they can, you can't even complain because it comes with the policy.<br>
<br>
