<br>
You can say hey lets petition a gm for PnP.  All the gm will do, if anything, will make the two(3? 4? 5?) groups of different people random for the zone.  You could be the group thats been there all day, or the group thats been there 5min and win or lose..and thats that.  Or the GM could just say its a zone like any other, whoever attacks it first gets dibs.  Won't that be fun?<br>
<br>
